{
  "stem": "18061.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Until one day they find out, as one of these friends, Berkowitz, he was a tailor, excellent tailor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they needed clothes, and a warm jacket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We did give them the money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They went over to fur store, boot stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He make it for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was something beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this guy went out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody went over to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where did you buy this, this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had a cousin over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told him the real story, that he has three Jews hidden, and one of them is a tailor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he make that for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And in his place, at daytime we were in that outside house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't a house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At night he took us to his house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He had a big room divided about like this here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How would you call that, from clothes, a divide?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A partition?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a partition.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the other side, that was a nice girl from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the boys were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were sitting in the place behind that curtain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We couldn't breathe, we couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Until this man came over, this cousin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, I know everything about you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I got a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Come over to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You make me one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we came over to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "According to where he lived, and the guy we were before, he was-- he was living in a villa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We came in over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The woman at the desk about money, let's say for 500 zloty, which according to our money was about $5.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She maked a meal like for a king.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Where in the other place, we paid 10 times as much, all we had is potatoes, cooked to be a roll that we shouldn't be able to eat much.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
